item.title: Are we going to die in a Few Days?
item.dc:creator: @Cole1497 Cole1497
item.description:
@Cole1497 wrote:

[quote="`Alec, post:2, topic:427368"][quote author=Cole1497 link=topic=530046.msg3870121#msg3870121 date=1325288566]
The calendar doesn’t end in 2012, the current b’aktun ends. It’s a cyclic calendar, it resets, and the calendar is cyclic. It doesn’t end, it only resets.
Also, the Mayans didn’t have leap years, so the reset of their calendar could have been a couple decades ago.

Take our calender for example. It ends on December 31st, 2011. Does that mean the end of the world is December 31st, 2011? Of course not.

Now, please, quit fucking believing this shit.
[/quote]

If you’re replying to my video;

  1. not my video
  2. it’s disproving 2012…[/quote]
    I know, I actually didn’t watch it until after I posted it, but I was talking to the OP, not you. Sorry for any confusion.
